This category of technologies describes various forms of digital communication and infrastructure, including technologies such as digital communication platforms, internet-based communication, digital marketing techniques, and digital payment systems. It also encompasses communication tools and platforms, such as messaging tools, telecommunication systems, and virtual communication platforms. Additionally, this category includes technologies related to internet connectivity, broadband access, and wireless communication, as well as digital inclusion initiatives and cross-regional collaboration tools. It also encompasses technologies for contact tracing, transmission routes research, and digital representation and information exchange. Overall, this category represents a wide range of technologies and tools that facilitate efficient and transparent communication, connectivity, and collaboration in various contexts, including green buildings and neighborhoods.